quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  34,1,"Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi ni khwa Nyasaye, ulia owebili mwikulu nende mushialo ne bibie, ne mwikulu okhwitsomibwa nokhukhwe, naye ni Owamachesi, Omumanyi muno."
  34,2,"Amanyile kenjilanga mushialo nende karulangamwo, nende kekhanga okhurula mwikulu nende kaninangamwo, naye ni Owetsimbabaasi muno, Omulesheli po."
  34,3,"Ne abakhayi baboola mbu: “Indukho eyo shilikhwitsila tawe.” Boola mbu: “Shineendio tawe? Nditsuba khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto ilibetsela, Omumanyi wakefisile, sishifisanga khuye tawe kata eshili nende obusiro shinga bweyindukusi, mwikulu nohomba khushialo, nohomba eshititi okhushila esho, nohomba eshikhongo muno, halali bioosi ebo bili mushitabu shinoosinjia.”"
  34,4,"Kho arunje balia abasuubila mana nibakhola ebikhole ebilayi. Abo balinyoola obulesheli nende omukabo kwoluyali."
  34,5,"Ne balia bakhalabana okhuyingasia ebimanyisio biefu, nibalola mbu betsa okhukhushila, abo balinyoola eshinyasio eshibii shiobululu."
  34,6,"Ne balia bahebwa obumanyi, bamanya mbu kalia keshibwa khwiwe okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ni katoto, nako kalunjisinjia khunjila ya Owamaani, witsomibungwa muno."
  34,7,"Ne balia abakhaya baboola mbu: “Koo, khubechesiekhwo Omusatsa ubaboolelanga mbu olwa muliba nimurandulwe (nimubolele) ebitonye ebitonye mbu mulikalusibwa mwaba ebiloonje ebiyiakha?"